  "texts": [
    "The absorbance spectra of AgF and AgF@AgM were collected using a JASCO V-770 spectrophotometer.",
    "Fluorescence microscopy.",
    "To test antifouling properties the AgF, AgF@AgM, and AgF@AgM@C10 were each placed separately inside a Luer cell, then a 1 mg mL -1 BSA-FITC solution was cycled through the cell at 5 mL min -1 for 10 min.",
    "Afterward, the samples were removed from the cell and thoroughly rinsed with deionized water.",
    "Fluorescence imaging was performed on a confocal microscope (Leica TCS SP5) and an appropriate light filter (450 nm excitation; 550 nm emission)."
